definitions.definition: A suburb of Leeds , West Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE2532 ) .
A village and civil parish in North Yorkshire , England , previously in Harrogate borough ( OS grid ref SE2147 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
